Prerequisites
=============

STLWRT requires the following packages:

 - The GLib, Pango, GdkPixbuf and cairo libraries. STLWRT requires at least
   GLib 2.28.0, Pango 1.20, GdkPixbuf 2.21.0 and cairo 1.6.0.

 - gobject-introspection 0.9.3 or newer.

 - If you build with accessibility support, then you'll also need ATK.


